Vivek Pai
Vivek Pai
Vivek Pai received his B.S. in Electrical Engineering from Rice University in 1991. He rejoined Rice University in 1993 and is currently working towards his M.S. and Ph.D. degrees from the department of Electrical and Computer Engineering.
He is currently working for Dr. Willy Zwaenepoel of the Computer Science Department, and is investigating buffer management for high-throughput systems. His other interests include operating systems and filesystem design.
He has also worked for a major oil company in its technical applications group, and he was one of the founders of Victory Software, an entertainment software company. His non-technical interests include racquetball, photography, and foreign films.
E-Mail:  vivek@rice.edu